  <diagram id="6yXPkgJIExrvWwakh_Nr" name="sequence barang keluar">
    <mxGraphModel dx="1935" dy="1043" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="827" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <UserObject label="" mermaidData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;sequenceDiagram\n    autonumber\n    actor Aktor as 🧑‍💼 Pengguna (Owner/Admin)\n    participant UI as 📱 StockOutPage\n    participant Prov as ⚙️ InventoryProvider\n    participant Serv as 🔧 FirestoreService\n    participant FB as ☁️ Cloud Firestore\n\n    Aktor -&gt;&gt; UI: Pilih Barang, Input Jumlah Keluar, Tanggal -&gt; Klik \&quot;Simpan\&quot;\n    UI -&gt;&gt; Prov: addStockOut(itemId, qtyOut, date, notes)\n    Prov -&gt;&gt; Serv: recordStockOutFIFO(itemId, qtyOut, date, notes)\n    \n    Serv -&gt;&gt; FB: collection(&#39;items&#39;).doc(itemId).get()\n    FB --&gt;&gt; Serv: Return Item Master (totalStock)\n    \n    alt totalStock &lt; qtyOut (Stok Tidak Cukup)\n        Serv --&gt;&gt; Prov: Throw Error \&quot;Stok Tidak Mencukupi\&quot;\n        Prov --&gt;&gt; UI: Tampilkan pesan error\n        UI --&gt;&gt; Aktor: Tampilkan peringatan merah \&quot;Stok Tidak Mencukupi\&quot;\n    else totalStock &gt;= qtyOut (Stok Cukup)\n        Serv -&gt;&gt; FB: collection(&#39;items/id/batches&#39;).where(remainingQty &gt; 0).orderBy(&#39;date&#39;, ASC).get()\n        FB --&gt;&gt; Serv: Return List of Available Batches [Oldest First]\n        \n        Note over Serv: Algoritma FIFO:&lt;br&gt;1. Loop dari batch tertua&lt;br&gt;2. Potong remainingQty&lt;br&gt;3. Hitung HPP = sum(qtyPotong * buyPrice)&lt;br&gt;4. Hitung Laba = (hargaJual * qtyOut) - HPP\n        \n        Note over Serv,FB: Eksekusi Firebase Batch Write\n        loop Untuk Setiap Batch yang Terpotong\n            Serv -&gt;&gt; FB: Update remainingQty pada Batch (atau Hapus jika 0)\n        end\n        Serv -&gt;&gt; FB: Simpan bukti ke collection(&#39;transactions&#39;) beserta rincian HPP &amp; Laba\n        Serv -&gt;&gt; FB: Update totalStock barang di master katalog\n        FB --&gt;&gt; Serv: Batch Commit Berhasil\n        \n        Serv --&gt;&gt; Prov: Konfirmasi Sukses + Ringkasan FIFO\n        Prov -&gt;&gt; Prov: notifyListeners()\n        Prov --&gt;&gt; UI: Transaksi Selesai\n        UI --&gt;&gt; Aktor: Tampilkan Notifikasi \&quot;Transaksi Keluar &amp; FIFO Berhasil Disimpan\&quot;\n    end&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;config&quot;: null&#xa;}" id="kzblnrlxoHZlFgTIfJZy-1">
          <mxCell connectable="0" parent="1" style="group;transparentBounds=1;editIcon=1;lockedGroup=0;groupPadding=20;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
