  <diagram id="oEx5-_qFMSnXeVuCbpz1" name="sequence Laporan Stok">
    <mxGraphModel dx="2580" dy="1390" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="827" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <UserObject label="" mermaidData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;sequenceDiagram\n    autonumber\n    actor Aktor as 🧑‍💼 Pengguna\n    participant UI as 📱 DashboardPage\n    participant Prov as ⚙️ InventoryProvider\n    participant Serv as 🔧 FirestoreService\n    participant FB as ☁️ Cloud Firestore\n\n    Aktor -&gt;&gt; UI: Membuka Halaman Utama (Dasbor / Laporan Stok)\n    UI -&gt;&gt; Prov: Listen to inventoryStream &amp; batchesStream\n    Prov -&gt;&gt; Serv: getRealtimeInventory()\n    Serv -&gt;&gt; FB: Listen to collection(&#39;items&#39;) &amp; subcollection(&#39;batches&#39;)\n    FB --&gt;&gt; Serv: Real-time Snapshot Data\n    Serv --&gt;&gt; Prov: Return Updated Inventory List\n\n    Note over Prov: Kalkulasi Dasbor secara Live:&lt;br&gt;1. Total Valuasi = sum(remainingQty * buyPrice)&lt;br&gt;2. Filter lowStockItems (stock &lt;= minimumStock)\n\n    Prov -&gt;&gt; Prov: notifyListeners()\n    Prov --&gt;&gt; UI: Kirim Data Ringkasan Valuasi &amp; Alert Low Stock\n    UI --&gt;&gt; Aktor: Tampilkan Kartu Valuasi Aset, Grafik Mutasi &amp; Peringatan Stok Menipis&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;config&quot;: null&#xa;}" id="-H2SQtobMEi2X4nfGiUN-1">
          <mxCell connectable="0" parent="1" style="group;transparentBounds=1;editIcon=1;lockedGroup=0;groupPadding=20;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry as="geometry" />
